pageContext.claim: “[Congress gives] me money for anything I want but as long as it has the word wall they don't want to do it. But I have the money, I'm building the wall.”
pageContext.analysis: Hardly. President Trump's health care proposal failed, he has had trouble getting disaster relief funding through Congress, and his infrastructure proposals stalled. Plus, now, the Democratic House of Representatives is reluctant to fund many of the president’s proposals.
